  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Chlorine</span> is created from Salt in a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Refiner</span>.<br>Chlorine can be mined directly from large underwater deposits. Mining requires use of an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Advanced Mining Laser</span>.",
