    "TencentChinese": "<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">氯</span>可采用<span class=\"name name-technology\">精炼机</span>从盐中制得。<br>氯可以直接从大型水下矿床中开采。开采需要使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">高级开采光束</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">氯</span>是以<span class=\"name name-technology\">精製機</span>從鹽萃取出來的。<br>氯可從大型水底資源產地開採出來。開採時需要用到<span class=\"name name-technology\">改良採礦雷射</span>。"
  },
